OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly dry, but cloudy start,
OL,6,Fbefore outbreaks of rain, locally
OL,7,Fheavy, spread eastwards across all
OL,8,Fparts during the morning. Winds light
OL,9,Finitially but becoming breezy at times
OL,10,Fduring the afternoon. Feeling humid,
OL,11,Fparticularly through the afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain will mostly clear
OL,14,Feastwards early in the evening,
OL,15,Falthough remaining cloudy for much of
OL,16,Fthe night with perhaps a few drizzly
OL,17,Fpatches at times. Mostly mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
