OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FMostly cloudy on Friday with a
OL,6,Ffew drizzly outbreaks possible in the
OL,7,Fmorning, but many areas remaining dry.
OL,8,FBreezy, especially along the coast.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,11,FGenerally dry through this period with
OL,12,Fpatchy cloud and sunny spells. Breezy
OL,13,Fon Saturday but winds falling light
OL,14,Ffor Sunday and Monday. Feeling warm,
OL,15,Fespecially in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
